COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to S.P. 776, L.D. 1981
1 SUMMARY
22 This amendment allows the proposed Emergency Medical Services Licensing Board
33 to direct an emergency medical services person to submit to a physical exam if the board
44 determines the emergency medical services person has diminished physical capabilities to
55 the extent the person cannot practice competently and with safety to patients.
66 FISCAL NOTE REQUIRED
77 (See attached)
